duties_responsibilities.duty: Join and grow a solo otolaryngology practice with a focus on serving minority communities in Los Angeles and Orange County.
Possibly build out and take ownership of the practice by delivering quality otolaryngology and related services.
No hospital call required, partnership track position with a defined timeline for partnership.
Fellowship training in H&N Surgery, Facial Plastics Surgery, Otology, or Rhinology is optional and not required.
Keen interest in learning the business of medicine is critical for success.
Completion of an accredited Otolaryngology residency and board certification or eligibility.

education_certification.credential: Completion of an accredited Otolaryngology residency and board certification or eligibility.
